               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1103" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1103" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1103" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1103" type="given" value="FELIX"></interp>FELIX LEWIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Covent-garden market. About a quarter past nine o'clock at night, on the 13th of August, I was with my wife in Totten-ham Court-road, and missed a handkerchief from my pocket—I ran after the prisoner, and caught him—the handkerchief has not been found.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184308210166"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1104" type="witnessName">
